name: Solemn Promise
description:
In a solemn promise, both partners will promise to live as long as they die, to be a king/queen in the life they will make.

Make the object in the crowd as an anomaly and symbolic of the couple who have tied the knot for life and death. Geese as a symbol of love and fidelty, because of their monogamous mating behavior and usually lasts a lifetime.
